ZH: 我会一直等你，直至你回来。
EN: I will wait for you until you come back.

ZH: 直至昨天，我才听到她的消息。
EN: I didn't hear from her until yesterday.

ZH: 他们一直工作，直至深夜。
EN: They worked non-stop until late at night.

ZH: 直至今天，我还没找到答案。
EN: Until today, I haven't found the answer.

ZH: 我会直至永远爱你。
EN: I will love you forever.

ZH: 直至我们解决了这个问题，我们不能休息。
EN: We cannot rest until we solve this problem.

ZH: 她直至临走前才告诉我这个好消息。
EN: She told me this good news just before she left.

ZH: 雨会一直下直至天黑。
EN: The rain will continue until dark.

ZH: 直至你说真心话，我才会相信你。
EN: I will not believe you until you tell me the truth.

ZH: 直至你道歉，我才会原谅你。
EN: I will not forgive you until you apologize.

ZH: 直至他们认识了这个事实，他们才相信。
EN: They didn't believe it until they knew the fact.

ZH: 直至他们醒来，我不能离开。
EN: I cannot leave until they wake up.

ZH: 我们要努力直至我们实现目标。
EN: We have to work hard until we achieve our goals.

ZH: 直至你背诵了古诗，你才能休息。
EN: You can rest only after you recite the ancient poem.

ZH: 他们直至边境才遇到敌人。
EN: They encountered the enemy only at the border.

ZH: 直至你解释清楚，我不会相信你。
EN: I won't believe you until you explain it clearly.

ZH: 直至你道歉，我不能忘记你的过错。
EN: I cannot forget your mistake until you apologize.

ZH: 直至我们被赶出去，我们不会离开。
EN: We won't leave until we are kicked out.

ZH: 直至收到消息，我不能安心休息。
EN: I cannot rest peacefully until I receive the news.

ZH: 直至他们得知真相，他们感到很震惊。
EN: They were shocked when they found out the truth.

ZH: 直至他们掌握了技巧，他们无法完成任务。
EN: They couldn't complete the task until they mastered the skills.
